            <p><span style="color:#0070C0"><b>Annex A - Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></span></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>17 </num>
              <p><span style="color:#000000">The Act extends and applies to the whole of the United Kingdom, including Northern Ireland.</span></p>
            </blockContainer>
            <table uk:widths="1.01in 1.24in 1.24in 1.24in 1.71in">
