                </th>
                <th>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000"><b>Extends to E &amp; W and applies to Wales?</b></span></p>
                </th>
                <th>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000"><b>Extends and applies to Scotland?</b></span></p>
                </th>
